cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on improving object detection precision for autonomous vehicles using a cooperative perception framework based on point cloud features. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by robotics (cs.RO) as autonomous vehicles are a key application area for robotics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for training and feature selection, which suggests categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) as likely possibilities.
